reviewText: If you enjoy. Laid back stories then this is. The DVD for you.the story with Victoria pribicapl in it was the. Worst I have ever seen her in.however it could have been the script which was really bad.
My wife and I were very pleased with the item.  It was just a described and arrived within the promised time.
They r very good movie's. i really enjoyed them.u guy's need to order them.

I love these bundles of Lifetime movies. My wife loves watching these on the lifetime movie network. I get them for her as a small gift for her birthday, valentine's day or Christmas.

She makes me watch them with her, but that is not the fault of the movies themselves.
These movies were drab and so-so. The colors were drab and a bit off. I watched all of these on cable but this dvd was not as good as the clearer picture on cable.

Not as advertised !  The product description says 3 disks. Guess what ? The order sent to me had all 3 movies crowded on just 1 disk.  I would describe it as being slightly grainy low budget vintage flicks that were a disappointment. Save your money.
Very good selection of interesting movies. Am pleased with the  three stories. REcomend to others.
the dvd itself was in good condition,..the movie however not really what i am used to seeing on lifetime.
nice dvd good for lifetime fans
